      "date": "2012-11-21 11:45:53.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/1bf037b8-33c9-11e2-89ef-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
